{"type": "article", "id": 17267, "title": "彩色户外椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-09T07:10:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060615271231OhHYEiz5C4UJwA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是放在户外椅子，来自意大利的二人组 adolini+simonini。沙发和躺椅都有一个类似藤条的扶手、靠背或者座位，是用铝管结构和合成皮带做的，成为一个提亮的部分，五颜六色，营造出轻松活泼的感觉。沙发上的垫子用了防水材料，可以放心地放在户外。<a href=\"http://www.adolinisimonini.com/adolini-simoniniflap-2.0.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144401X2OEzxnmCv0tuoiS.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"528\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64547677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144401xeos931ThXvYKN8R.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144402Q8KYyXPBO63kFbjr.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144403wbEvL4NK6exSCpti.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"513\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62713936\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144403SUnV4g9r0hOGmw35.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"608\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74327628\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}